isValidSignature.t.sol
├─ given the contract is paused
│  └─ it should revert
└─ given the contract is not paused
   ├─ given the bid function was entered
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ given the bid function was not entered
      ├─ when the order ID is invalid
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the order ID is valid
         ├─ when the auction is not valid (non allowlisted asset or auction not started)
